{"tid":906754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"西鐵月票一問","createTime":"2018-11-18T08:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T11:43:37.000Z","uid":75952,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fa2b928eca5e09fbb1cf1a76b0585b40d93837be","tid":906754,"uid":75952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T08:55:09.000Z","msg":"阿媽用開西鐵月票舊制380元好多年，以前佢用個人八達卡買<br />\n<br />\n因為今年65歲，個人八達通自動變左做老人八達通<br />\n<br />\n咁佢想將舊的380元月票留俾我妹妹用，打算取消老人八達通或解除個人八達通與月票的捆綁，但地鐵職員話唔得<br />\n<br />\n想問巴打有冇其他方法或建議？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c150c6d27cf09de6e58dbe6063bc22652be284","tid":906754,"uid":39878,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:37:22.000Z","msg":"用腦諗下都知唔得啦 依家玩世襲制咩"},{"pid":"31a70feda28345607b9f8757e1c72f2b95313f2d","tid":906754,"uid":25794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"20c150c6d27cf09de6e58dbe6063bc22652be284","tid":906754,"uid":39878,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:37:22.000Z","msg":"用腦諗下都知唔得啦 依家玩世襲制咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T11:43:37.000Z","msg":"永續"}]}